<!-- PJG ITAG l=84 g=1 f=1 -->
Paperwork Reduction Act 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
Certain sections of these proposed regulations contain information collection requirements which are subject
to review and approval by OMB under the Paperwork Reduction Act of 1980 (44 U.S.C. chapter 35). The proposed revisions
for the title IV&hyph;A child care programs will produce only minor changes and additions to the State Supportive
Services Plan (ACF&hyph;106). 
