<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
In June of 1991, EPA entered into a proposed consent decree in a lawsuit filed by the Environmental Defense Fund, 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
et al.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
