<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
Today's proposed listings will be promulgated pursuant to HSWA. HSWA requirements are applicable in authorized
States at the same time as in unauthorized States. Therefore, EPA will regulate the wastes being proposed today until
States are authorized to regulate these wastes. Once these regulations are promulgated in a final rule by EPA, the
Agency will apply these Federal regulations to these wastes and to their management in both authorized and unauthorized
States. 
