status may, under certain conditions, qualify for an exemption from the performance of assessment work and the payment
of maintenance fees. See &sect;&sect;3833.1&hyph;7(e)(2) and 3851.6 of this title. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
