claims and sites located upon National Park System lands: 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(1) The claimant has received a declaration of taking or a notice of intent to take from the National Park Service pursuant
to sections 6 and 7 of the Act of September 28, 1976, as amended (16 U.S.C. 1905, 1906) or the Act of December 2, 1980, as
amended (16 U.S.C. 3192); or the claimant has otherwise been denied access by the United States to his/her mining claims
or sites on National Park Service lands. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
